              Federal judge in Florida tosses Trump's $15B defamation lawsuit against New York Times


              US District Judge Steven Merryday rules that Trump has 28 days to file an amended complaint















    <img class="Image" alt="Britain Trump" src="https://ewscripps.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/e3e68e4/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x576+0+54/resize/1280x720!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fewscripps.brightspotcdn.com%2F73%2Fb4%2F6ce9c71a451bb7f488b52b3a6bc0%2Fap25262001422310.jpg" />





