              South Florida officer, deputy capture 14-foot Burmese python along busy road


              Python caught outside tire shop in the village of Pinecrest in Miami-Dade County















    <img class="Image" alt="A deputy and a Pinecrest police officer show off a 14-foot python they captured." src="https://ewscripps.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/5277451/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1280x720+0+0/resize/1280x720!/quality/90/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fewscripps-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F2f%2Fd4%2F0404487549d1928847663f42ec11%2Fpython.jpg" />





